#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:7
msgid ""
"The Mattermost for Microsoft Teams integration enables you to break "
"through siloes in a mixed Mattermost and Teams environment by forwarding "
"real-time chat notifications from Teams to Mattermost."
msgstr ""
"Mattermost for Microsoft Teams 통합을 통해 Teams에서 Mattermost로 실시간 채팅 알림을 전달하여 "
"Mattermost와 Teams가 혼합된 환경에서 정보 격차를 해소할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:-1
msgid ""
"Mattermost for Microsoft Teams integration forwards real-time chat "
"notifications from Teams to Mattermost."
msgstr ""
"Mattermost for Microsoft Teams 통합은 Teams에서 Mattermost로 실시간 채팅 알림을 전달합니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:17
msgid "Connect your Mattermost account to your Microsoft Teams account"
msgstr "Mattermost 계정을 Microsoft Teams 계정에 연결하기"

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:20
msgid ""
"Your System Administrator must install and enable the :doc:`Mattermost "
"for Microsoft Teams integration </integrate/microsoft-teams-sync>` and "
"ensure :ref:`support for notifications is enabled <configure/plugins-"
"configuration-settings:sync notifications>` in order for you to connect "
"your account and recieve chat notifications."
msgstr ""
"시스템 관리자는 계정을 연결하고 채팅 알림을 받을 수 있도록 :doc:`Mattermost for Microsoft Teams 통합 "
"</integrate/microsoft-teams-sync>` 을 설치하고 활성화하고 :ref:`알림 지원이 활성화되어 있는지 "
"<configure/plugins-configuration-settings:sync notifications>` 확인해야 합니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:23
msgid ""
"Once the integration is installed and configured by a System "
"Administrator, you can connect your Mattermost user account to your "
"Microsoft Teams account. You only need to complete this step once."
msgstr ""
"시스템 관리자가 통합을 설치하고 구성하면 Mattermost 사용자 계정을 Microsoft Teams 계정에 연결할 수 있습니다. "
"이 단계는 한 번만 완료하면 됩니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:25
msgid "Log into Mattermost using your credentials."
msgstr "자격 증명을 사용하여 Mattermost에 로그인하세요."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:26
msgid ""
"In any channel, run the ``/msteams connect`` slash command, and select "
"the resulting link."
msgstr ""
"모든 채널에서 ``/msteams connect`` 슬래시 명령을 실행하고 결과 링크를 선택하세요."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:27
msgid ""
"Authenticate with Microsoft Teams using the email address matching your "
"account in Mattermost."
msgstr ""
"Mattermost의 계정과 일치하는 이메일 주소를 사용하여 Microsoft Teams로 인증하세요."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:29
msgid "Mattermost will confirm when your account is connected."
msgstr "계정이 연결되면 Mattermost가 확인 메시지를 표시합니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:31
msgid ""
"Once you've connected your Mattermost account to your Microsoft Teams "
"account, when you're offline or away from Microsoft Teams, any messages "
"you receive in a chat or group chat in Microsoft Teams will display in "
"Mattermost as a notification and include a link to open the chat in "
"Microsoft Teams to continue the conversation. These notifications won't "
"appear if you've been recently active in Teams."
msgstr ""
"Mattermost 계정을 Microsoft Teams 계정에 연결하면 오프라인이거나 Microsoft Teams에 접속하지 않은 상태에서 "
"Microsoft Teams의 채팅이나 그룹 채팅에서 받은 메시지가 Mattermost에 알림으로 표시되며 대화를 계속하기 위해 "
"Microsoft Teams에서 채팅을 열 수 있는 링크가 포함됩니다. 최근에 Teams에서 활동한 경우에는 이러한 알림이 "
"표시되지 않습니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:-1
msgid "An example of a chat message notification."
msgstr "채팅 메시지 알림의 예시입니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:37
msgid "Manage notification settings"
msgstr "알림 설정 관리"

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:39
msgid ""
"Manage your Mattermost notification settings for the Microsoft Teams "
"integration at any time in **Settings** > **Plugin Preferences**"
msgstr ""
"**설정** > **플러그인 환경설정** 에서 언제든지 Microsoft Teams 통합을 위한 Mattermost 알림 설정을 관리할 수 "
"있습니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:-1
msgid ""
"Manage notification settings for the Microsoft Teams integration in "
"Account Settings > Plugin Preferences"
msgstr ""
"계정 설정 > 플러그인 환경설정에서 Microsoft Teams 통합을 위한 알림 설정을 관리할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:46
msgid ""
"You can run the following :ref:`slash commands <collaborate/run-slash-"
"commands:run slash commands>` to manage your integration settings by "
"typing the commands into the Mattermost message text box, and selecting "
"**Send**:"
msgstr ""
"Mattermost 메시지 텍스트 상자에 명령어를 입력하고 **전송** 을 선택하여 다음 :ref:`슬래시 명령어 "
"<collaborate/run-slash-commands:run slash commands>` 를 실행하여 통합 설정을 관리할 수 있습니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:48
msgid ""
"``/msteams connect``: Connect your Mattermost account to Microsoft Teams "
"account."
msgstr ""
"``/msteams connect``: Mattermost 계정을 Microsoft Teams 계정에 연결합니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:49
msgid ""
"``/msteams disconnect``: Disconnect your Mattermost account from "
"Microsoft Teams account."
msgstr "``/msteams disconnect``: Mattermost 계정을 Microsoft Teams 계정에서 연결 해제합니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:50
msgid "``/msteams status``: Show your current connection status."
msgstr "``/msteams status``: 현재 연결 상태를 표시합니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:51
msgid ""
"``/msteams notifications on|off``: Change your current notifications "
"settings."
msgstr "``/msteams notifications on|off``: 현재 알림 설정을 변경합니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:54
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "자주 묻는 질문"

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:57
msgid "How does the integration determine when to send chat notifications?"
msgstr "통합 기능은 언제 채팅 알림을 보낼지 어떻게 결정하나요?"

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:59
msgid ""
"Chat notifications are sent in real-time whenever you're not active in "
"Microsoft Teams and receive a chat or group chat. Mattermost uses your "
"online status in Teams to determine if a chat notification should be "
"delivered. Mattermost delivers notifications if you appear **Away** or "
"**Offline** in Microsoft Teams, so the default behavior for when "
"notifications will be delivered depends on the client you typically use "
"to access Microsoft Teams:"
msgstr ""
"Microsoft Teams에서 활동하지 않을 때 채팅이나 그룹 채팅을 받으면 실시간으로 채팅 알림이 전송됩니다. Mattermost는 "
"Teams에서의 온라인 상태를 사용하여 채팅 알림을 전달해야 하는지 결정합니다. Microsoft Teams에서 **자리비움** 또는 "
"**오프라인** 상태로 표시되면 Mattermost가 알림을 전달하므로, 알림이 전달되는 시점의 기본 동작은 일반적으로 Microsoft "
"Teams에 접속하는 데 사용하는 클라이언트에 따라 달라집니다:"

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:61
msgid ""
"Web browser: Mattermost delivers notifications when you've not had "
"activity in your Microsoft Teams browser tab for 5 minutes or more, when "
"the browser tab is closed, or when you mark yourself as **Offline** in "
"Microsoft Teams."
msgstr ""
"웹 브라우저: Microsoft Teams 브라우저 탭에서 5분 이상 활동이 없거나, 브라우저 탭이 닫혔거나, Microsoft "
"Teams에서 **오프라인** 으로 표시한 경우 Mattermost가 알림을 전달합니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:62
msgid ""
"Desktop app: Mattermost delivers notifications when you've not had "
"activity at your computer for 5 minutes or more, when the Microsoft Teams"
" desktop app is closed, or when you mark yourself as **Offline** in "
"Microsoft Teams."
msgstr "데스크톱 앱: 컴퓨터에서 5분 이상 활동이 없거나, Microsoft Teams 데스크톱 앱이 닫혔거나, Microsoft Teams에서 **오프라인** 으로 표시한 경우 Mattermost가 알림을 전달합니다."

#: ../../source/collaborate/collaborate-within-connected-microsoft-teams.rst:64
msgid ""
"In order to avoid double notifications, Mattermost won't deliver chat "
"notifications when your availability is set to **Available**, **Busy**, "
"**Do not disturb**, or **Be right back** in Microsoft Teams."
msgstr "중복 알림을 방지하기 위해 Microsoft Teams에서 상태가 **사용 가능**, **바쁨**, **방해 금지** 또는 **곧 돌아옴** 으로 설정된 경우 Mattermost는 채팅 알림을 전달하지 않습니다."

